    "featureBullets": [
      "- UCANBE Classic White Cream to Powder Face & Body Paint Foundation has a smoothly and velvety consistency that glides on like cream yet settles down to a matte finish. White Face Makeup Paint is safe and non-toxic for people of all ages, seniors and youngsters, adults and kids. Suitable for both face and body painting starters and enthusiasts on different occasions such as stage, cosplay conferences, parties and more.",
      "- Our white face and body paint, with silky foundation-like texture, is easy to use and will give a full coverage. Easy to apply and blend for various fantastic makeup looks, such as classic clown or Joker makeup, pale vampire Makeup, ghost makeup, pop art makeup, skull or skeleton costume makeup.White makeup to use alone or mix with other colors for all Halloween makeup.",
      "- UCANBE white face painting foundation has intense white color and delivers fully opaque and even coverage. White greasepaint has long lasting staying power which are suitable for eyes, face and body art painting.",
      "- Easy use and easy cleaning off. For application, you can apply with paint brushes(including flat brushes, detail line brushes), foam applicators or your fingers to create the desired graphs or images. And at the end of the day, removes the white paints easily with some makeup remover, cleansing cream or facial cleanser, then use soap & water to finish the cleaning process.",
      "- All UCANBE cream foundation paints are manufactured using cosmetic-grade quality ingredients, non-toxic, fragrance-free and paraben-free, suitable for delicate and sensitive skin, kids and adults. It won't itch or irritate your skin.\u3010NOTICE\u3011As with all cosmetics, we advise that a small skin patch test is done before face painting as everyone's skin is different."
    ],
