          "reviewTitle": "quality",
          "reviewText": "I am a cosplayer and i swear by this stuff. When you apply in thin layers and you pair it with a setting powder and a setting spray there is very little cracking or flaking. Lasts all con and doesnt make me break out too bad. The compact case makes it easy to take along with you for touch ups and keeps it sealed for later use. Looks cute too.",
